      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's huge, like maybe 50km across? and the pressure is dropping fast. i can literally feel the vibration in my chest when the wind gusts. if i use the formula you gave, how do i account for the humidity? i noticed that when the air gets thicker/more humid, i have to pitch my voice slightly higher to get the same effect on the wind. can you adjust the calculation so i don't miss the target?",
      "source": "evaluator"
